                point, I had enough of an outline of what features were wanted and had an idea of what the user flow
                should be. As a result, I was able to make a medium-fidelity wireframe which is shown in the first
                embedded Figma file.<br><br>
                After further meetings and changes, we moved forward with a high-fidelity prototype which is shown below
